import re
def get_gu(text):
    text = re.sub('(.+\s)(.+)', r'\2', text)
    return text

df_students_s[''] = df_students_s[''].map(get_gu)

def get_num(data):
    data = re.sub('(\d+)(.+)', r'\1', data)
    return int(data)

df_students_s[''] = df_students_s['()'].map(get_num)
